{"tid":2286808,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿里在美遭集體興訟","createTime":"2020-11-15T09:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T10:26:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"984177e1e1e334f911a51510d7a2747b4dfbe4e3","tid":2286808,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201115/Q45PCYMNKVEB7KKKSNEEPPUFGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201115%2FQ45PCYMNKVEB7KKKSNEEPPUFGQ%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEy%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=8be1b57b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201115%2FQ45PCYMNKVEB7KKKSNEEPPUFGQ%2F&h=baa05ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201115/Q45PCYMNKVEB7KKKSNEEPPUFGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n阿里在美遭集體興訟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-0DN8GfulgemUEBR3pYyFbLzF-o=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V2NVNOHNABC75NGRWTS354QDQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-0DN8GfulgemUEBR3pYyFbLzF-o%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV2NVNOHNABC75NGRWTS354QDQM.jpg&h=c6148879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有投資者指控阿里在螞蟻上市過程作出錯誤陳述或誤導聲明。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】阿里巴巴（9988）當黑，螞蟻上市失敗後續有餘波。彭博報道指出，一位名為Laura Ciccarello的投資者上周五到紐約聯邦法院入稟，指控阿里、阿里行政總裁張勇及財務總監武衛涉及在螞蟻上市的過程中，作出錯誤陳述或誤導聲明。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：標指創收市新高  高盛摩通鬥「牛」索羅斯吸新經濟股<br />\n<br />\nCiccarello指出，阿里持螞蟻33%權益，而外界預期螞蟻可上市集資345億美元，最後卻傳因為中國監管機構向螞蟻總裁「照肺」，上市工作遭到暫緩。Ciccarello還投訴，螞蟻在11月3日解釋暫緩決定時表示，集團或因文件問題未能滿足上市資格或披露要求，阿里隨後在美股跌8%至285美元的水平，原告及其他群體因被告的處事錯誤與疏忽，以及公司證券市值大幅下挫，而蒙受重大損失。<br />\n<br />\n阿里上周五在港收報257港元，較擱置螞蟻上市前高位累跌約17%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2015年被控 賠19億和解<br />\n<br />\n阿里已非首次被投資者進行集體訴訟。。。。。。。。。。。。，阿里決定賠2.5億美元（約19.4億港元）進行和解。"},{"pid":"ff0931298dfeb80d02916e792c2f4f37488b64f7","tid":2286808,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad39c41a46c88d8fcd59e8664fa1bac041ac498","tid":2286808,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7896cf62d1accab52728e674913ebb0f3897a0f","tid":2286808,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又跌"},{"pid":"e11bbfc251e4b5f69e3b3bf267d44354ae5def6f","tid":2286808,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"財務總監武衛<br />\n<br />\n姓武 真係好難改名  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}